code: @Override public Instant deserialize(JsonParser jsonParser, DeserializationContext deserializationContext) throws IOException {     try {         Long unixTimestamp = Long.parseLong(jsonParser.getText()).         return Instant.ofEpochSecond(unixTimestamp).     } catch (Exception e) {         log.warn("Unable to deserialize the unix timestamp {}", jsonParser.getText(), e).         return null.     } }
